## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="eacc6-113"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A>返回时，应通过验证参数是否为来执行边界检查 `pointer` `null` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eacc6-113">When <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> returns, you should perform bounds checking by verifying that the `pointer` parameter is `null`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="eacc6-114">如果不是 `null` ，则必须 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.ReleasePointer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 在 (CER) 的受约束的执行区域中调用方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eacc6-114">If it is not `null`, you must call the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.ReleasePointer%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method in a constrained execution region (CER).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="eacc6-115"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> 调用 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.DangerousAddRef%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法并公开指针。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eacc6-115"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> calls the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeHandle.DangerousAddRef%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method and exposes the pointer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="eacc6-116">与 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.Read%2A> 方法不同，它不会更改指针的当前位置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eacc6-116">Unlike the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.Read%2A> method, it does not change the current position of the pointer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="eacc6-117">下面的示例演示如何使用 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> 方法：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eacc6-117">The following example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.SafeBuffer.AcquirePointer%2A> method:</span></span>  
  
```  
byte* pointer = null;  
RuntimeHelpers.PrepareConstrainedRegions();  
try {  
    MySafeBuffer.AcquirePointer(ref pointer);  
    // Use pointer here, with your own bounds checking.  
    }  
finally {  
    if (pointer != null)  
        MySafeBuffer.ReleasePointer();  
    }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="eacc6-118">如果强制转换 `pointer` (这是一个指向字节的指针) 作为指向不同类型 (T \* ) 的指针，则可能会出现指针对齐问题。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eacc6-118">If you cast `pointer` (which is a pointer to a byte) as a pointer to a different type (T\*), you may have pointer alignment issues.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="eacc6-119">必须负责对此指针进行所有边界检查。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eacc6-119">You must take responsibility for all bounds checking with this pointer.</span></span>

